                            <comment id="13193883" author="alex.parvulescu" created="Thu, 26 Jan 2012 15:09:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Proposed patch.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Replaced tr.find(&apos;td:eq(4)&apos;) with tr.children(&apos;td:eq(4)&apos;).&lt;br/&gt;
This handles the case where there are embedded tables and the selector can go awry.&lt;/p&gt;

